se en conduisant, se dessine une situation qui parait inextricable.\r\n\r\nJe recommande ce film pour la remarquable performance de Tom Hardy mais aussi car le personnage qu‚Äôil interpr√®te a un accent √† la fois int√©ressant et facile √† comprendre.\r\nVous pouvez acheter le DVD en vostfr <a href=\"http://www.amazon.fr/gp/product/B00OGQUB62/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1642&amp;creative=6746&amp;creativeASIN=B00OGQUB62&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=frenchencom-21\" target=\"_blank\">ici</a>\r\n\r\n<em>It is rather difficult to tell you about this movie without revealing too much. What I can say is that this drama is filmed like a thriller yet the whole action is taking place in a car ! Locke, a hard-working and honest family man, someone who seems to have it all, leaves to an unknow destination. But as he keeps making more and more phone calls while driving, a situation that seems quite inextricable starts to unveil. I would recommend waching this movie for Tom hardy‚Äôs remarkable performance but also because his character has an interesting yet easy to understand accent.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Calvary </strong></span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdE3-lY6_do\" target=\"_blank\">Trailer</a>\r\n\r\nCalvary est un drame √† l‚Äôhumour tr√®s noir et qui s‚Äôadresse d√©finitivement √† un public adulte. L‚Äôhistoire tourne autour d‚Äôun pasteur Irlandais et de ses ouailles qui sont pour la plupart des fr√©quentations vraiment peu recommandables. La vie personnelle du h√©ros est √©galement loin d‚Äô√™tre un fleuve tranquille : il doit soutenir moralement sa fille qui est suicidaire et faire face √† des menaces de mort.\r\nAu casting on retrouve Chris O‚Äôdowd, Kelly Reilly (l‚Äôauberge espagnol, sherlock Holmes) et Brendan Gleeson, acteur dont le nom n‚Äôest pas si connu en France bien qu‚Äôil ait eu une filmographie impressionnante : Braveheart, Gangs of New York, 28 jours plus tard, Troie, Harry Potter, etc‚Ä¶Ce film a √©t√© pr√©sent√© au festival Sundance et au festival de Berlin et a √©t√© globalement acclam√© par la critique.\r\n\r\nIl est disponible sur <a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/product/B00JO9O1WG/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1634&amp;creative=6738&amp;creativeASIN=B00JO9O1WG&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=frenchencom06-21\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon.uk</a> (sans sous-titres) en attendant sa sortie en dvd en France.\r\n\r\n<em>Calvary is a drama with a very black humour which is definitively targeted at an adult audience. The story revolves around an Irish clergyman and his parish members who mostly are shady characters. The hero‚Äôs personnal life is also far from being a walk in the park : he has to offer moral support to his suicidal daughter and cope with death threats.</em>\r\n<em> The cast includes Chris O‚Äôdowd (again), Kelly Reilly (The Spanish apartment, Sherlock Holmes) and Brendan Glesson, an actor whose name is rather unknown in France even though he has an impressive filmography : Braveheart, Gangs of New York, 28 days later, Troy, Harry Potter, etc‚Ä¶ The film has been screened at Sundance and Berlin Film Festivals and has mostly been acclaimed by the critics.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Thriller :</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>¬†Les poings contre les murs/Starred up </strong></span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=62kCfi9T7KE\" target=\"_blank\">Trailer </a>\r\n\r\nCe film offre une vision parfois tr√®s d√©rangeante de l‚Äôunivers carc√©ral et comporte plusieurs sc√®nes de violence tr√®s explicites. Il est donc interdit au moins de 12 ans. En anglais, Starred up est une expression employ√©e par le personnel travaillant dans les prisons pour d√©signer un mineur envoy√© en centre de d√©tention pour adultes. C‚Äôest le cas du personnage principal de ce film, Eric, un jeune d√©linquant de 19 ans. A l‚Äôaide d‚ÄôOliver, le psychologue de la prison, il d√©c