d new paths to many artists. The movie unveils a lesser-known part of his life which is his affairs with his housekeeper and a seaside pension landlady. This long and rather contemplative movie is definitely not a good fit for those who crave action and thrill but will surely delight those who are interested in an faithfull portrayal of a complex artist and human being.</em>\r\n<em> Timothy Spall won the palme for Best Actor for this movie.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nVoil√† pour la premi√®re partie de ma liste. J\'esp√®re qu\'au moins un de ces titres vous inspire et n\'h√©sitez pas, vous aussi, √† sugg√©rer des films que vous avez appr√©ci√© en 2014 !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4><strong><a href=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8292279473_e774337a0d.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-411 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8292279473_e774337a0d-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"8292279473_e774337a0d\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></strong></h4>','Boostez votre compr√©hension orale : une petite liste de films Britanniques et Am√©ricains sortis en 2014 (1√®re partie)','','inherit','open','open','','396-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 11:45:06','2015-03-10 10:45:06','',396,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/blog/2015/03/10/396-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(424,1,'2015-03-18 01:12:57','2015-03-18 00:12:57','','respire_cadre','','inherit','open','open','','respire_cadre','','','2015-03-18 01:12:57','2015-03-18 00:12:57','',414,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/respire_cadre.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(425,1,'2015-03-18 01:16:41','2015-03-18 00:16:41','','index','','inherit','open','open','','index','','','2015-03-18 01:16:41','2015-03-18 00:16:41','',414,'http://www.frenchenglishservices.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/index.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(426,1,'2015-03-18 01:19:43','2015-03-18 00:19:43','','inex','','inherit','open','open','','inex','